<?php $__env->startSection('content'); ?><p>She has been open about the realities of breastfeeding her son Apollo, 13 months.</p>

<p>And Myleene Klass was again giving her fans an insight into life as a working and breastfeeding mother as she took to Instagram to share a sweet snap. </p>

<p>The radio presenter, 42, posted the snap just hours before heading to work at Global Studios while sporting a typically stunning ensemble. </p>

<p>Stunner: Myleene Klass was seen heading to work at Global Studios while sporting a typically stunning ensemble</p>

<p>Myleene looked stunning as she headed to work in the rust coloured ensemble which featured a soft material and was layered under a camisole. </p>

<p>She clutched one of her envy-inducing Chanel handbags and donned stylish over-sized sunglasses to complete the glamour. </p>

<p>Prior to work, she was tucked up in bed breasfeeding Apollo, a moment she captured and shared with her adoring 367,000 Instagram followers.  </p>

<p>Over the weekend, Myleene revealed that she had broken the strap on her white summer maxi dress because her 'breastfeeding boobies are heavy'.</p>

<p>Happy days: She was again giving her fans an insight into life as a working and breastfeeding mother as she took to Instagram to share a sweet snap</p>

<p>Elegant: Myleene looked stunning as she headed to work in the rust coloured ensemble which featured a soft material and was layered under a camisole</p>

<p>Working hard: She was headed for another day at Global</p>

<p>She took to Instagram to share her outfit mishap as she revealed how the air conditioning in the Smooth Radio studios had also stopped working.</p>

<p>Speaking on her Instagram Stories, Myleene said: 'Just got into work my strap has broken as has the air con but we are playing chilled out songs!' </p>

<p>Myleene's latest appearance came after her recent social media run-in with a troll who claimed her boyfriend Simon Motson will cheat on her. </p>

<p>A vision: She clutched one of her envy-inducing Chanel handbags and donned stylish over-sized sunglasses to complete the glamour</p>

<p>Off we go: Prior to work, she was tucked up in bed breasfeeding Apollo, a moment she captured and shared with her adoring 367,000 Instagram followers</p>

<p>The broadcaster recently posted a gallery of sweet images with the PR executive beau, 45, to celebrate five years since they had met.</p>

<p>However a troll wrote underneath: 'Not long before this one cheats on you. Dear oh dear, heading for the lawyers are we?'</p>

<p>In a pointed response, she fired back: 'He wishes! Cheating exes usually get a house, a car and a fat pay-off, in what appeared to be a dig at her ex-husband Graham Quinn, who left her on her 34th birthday in 2012.</p>

<p>The heartbreaking incident came just six months after the couple's wedding, but they had been together for 11 years at the time, after meeting when Graham became the bodyguard for Myleene's pop group Hear'Say in 2001.</p>

<p>Hitting back: Myleene's latest appearance came after her recent social media run-in with a troll who claimed her boyfriend Simon Motson will cheat on her</p>

<p>Cruel: However a troll wrote underneath: 'Not long before this one cheats on you. Dear oh dear, heading for the lawyers are we?'</p>

<p>The former couple are parents to two daughters, Ava, 13, and Hero, nine and Myleene was devastated to learn that he had secretly bought a bachelor pad for himself – meaning that he must have been planning his departure for some time.</p>

<p>The TV star was said to be blindsided by the split after supporting Graham, but it was never publicly confirmed if he cheated.</p>

<p>Myleene is now in a happy relationship with PR exec Simon who she began dating in 2015 after being introduced by two mutual friends, and the pair welcomed their first child together, son Apollo, in August last year.</p>

<p>Hitting out: The TV star was said to be blindsided by the split after supporting Graham, but it was never publicly confirmed if he cheated</p>
